Dobie ?

46:13.905 --> 46:14.940
[ Whimpering,
barking ]

46:14.973 --> 46:17.275
Dobie !
Dobie !

46:21.212 --> 46:23.915
[ Horn honks,
tires screech ]

46:26.885 --> 46:29.855
[ Horns honking ]
Dobie !

46:31.923 --> 46:33.791
[ Horns honking ]
Dobie !

46:34.392 --> 46:37.495
[ Screaming ]

46:41.967 --> 46:44.135
- [ Screaming ]
- [ Glass shatters ]

46:54.279 --> 46:57.082
[ Panting, moaning ]

46:57.115 --> 46:59.150
[ Chattering ]

47:19.637 --> 47:22.240
So what's it gonna be,
paul ?

47:27.946 --> 47:30.015
Stapleton ?

47:35.786 --> 47:37.822
[ Gulls crying ]

47:59.777 --> 48:01.879
[ Laughing ]

48:47.258 --> 48:49.327
[ Animal growling ]

48:53.098 --> 48:55.300
[ Growling continues ]

49:08.213 --> 49:11.016
[ Barking, snarling ]

49:25.296 --> 49:26.897
She just woke up.

49:38.143 --> 49:41.279
Stand away
from the door, please.

49:41.312 --> 49:45.016
I don't know who you are,
and I don't know
where I am,

49:45.050 --> 49:47.518
but I know that I'm
being held here...

49:47.552 --> 49:50.255
Against my will, and
you can't do that, and
I want to use the telephone.

49:50.288 --> 49:51.789
I'd like you
to sit on the bed.

49:51.822 --> 49:55.326
I just found
my husband's dead body,
and I want to use the phone !

49:55.360 --> 49:58.063
You can use the phone
after you've seen
Dr. Silverman.

49:58.096 --> 50:01.266
What the hell
is this place ?
This is stapleton hospital.

50:01.299 --> 50:03.968
This is Rosco,
and I'm nurse Floyd.
I'm in charge of this wing.

50:04.001 --> 50:08.306
Well, fuck both of you.
I want Silverman
in here now.

50:08.339 --> 50:10.641
And I want to use
the phone !
You're not listening.

50:10.675 --> 50:13.111
I just explained
about the phone.

50:13.844 --> 50:15.313
Why don't you understand ?

50:15.346 --> 50:17.948
I was just in a hotel room
at the carlton hotel,

50:17.982 --> 50:21.552
and in room 401
you will find the body
of my murdered husband.

50:21.586 --> 50:23.588
- just check it out.
- you want me to put her
on the bed ?

50:23.621 --> 50:26.457
- I'm just gonna put you--
- no ! don't touch me !

50:26.491 --> 50:27.592
Is there someone
I can call ?
I'll kill you !

50:27.625 --> 50:29.827
Can I call someone
for you ?

50:29.860 --> 50:31.296
Yes. Call
the fucking police...

50:31.329 --> 50:33.831
And tell them
that my husband's being
eaten by a dog...

50:33.864 --> 50:36.367
In a hotel room
in Hammond.

50:36.401 --> 50:37.902
[ Sobbing ]

50:39.437 --> 50:41.506
[ Sobbing, laughing ]

50:41.539 --> 50:43.174
Why are you laughing,
Claire ?

50:46.010 --> 50:48.546
'Cause...

50:48.579 --> 50:50.948
The bastard's
in my head.

50:50.981 --> 50:54.285
He's fucked up
my brain.

50:54.319 --> 50:56.887
And now he's
murdered my husband.

50:59.590 --> 51:00.758
Oh.

51:02.960 --> 51:04.662
Oh, god !

51:04.695 --> 51:07.365
It's happening again !
What's happening,
Claire ?

51:07.398 --> 51:10.601
What ?
What are they doing ?

51:11.536 --> 51:14.139
No ! no !

51:14.172 --> 51:16.207
[ Claire screaming ]

51:21.912 --> 51:24.014
[ Rosco ]
We're here to help.

51:27.518 --> 51:28.953
How is she ?

51:30.521 --> 51:35.160
Terrible.
I'm gonna sell this house.

51:36.527 --> 51:38.963
I need to get her
a new shrink.

51:40.165 --> 51:42.167
Want a second opinion ?

51:42.200 --> 51:45.770
Yeah.
I want 20 of 'em.

51:45.803 --> 51:49.039
Whatever it takes to get her
out of that place.
[ Phone ringing ]

51:56.113 --> 51:59.550
There's a lady on the phone.
Says she found dobie
near some hotel.

52:01.552 --> 52:03.988
Hello ?
[ Vivian ]
Mr. Cooper ?

52:12.096 --> 52:14.765
[ Groggily ]
Doctor, don't-don't let
paul go to the hotel.

52:16.867 --> 52:19.570
Don't let him go.

52:19.604 --> 52:23.941
Is this a real hotel ?
It doesn't matter.
It's the carlton.

52:23.974 --> 52:26.377
It's by the ocean
in hammond.

52:26.411 --> 52:30.515
When were you there ?
Last night,
room 401.

52:30.548 --> 52:33.551
So it's not real.
You dreamed it.

52:34.952 --> 52:38.189
Was it day or night ?
It's daytime.
Please call him.

52:51.669 --> 52:53.204
[ Silverman ]
Does he meet someone there ?

52:53.238 --> 52:57.442
He goes to find Dobie.
Is Dobie a woman,
Claire ?

52:57.475 --> 52:58.876
[ Groaning ]

53:02.480 --> 53:04.815
He's a fucking dog.

53:16.093 --> 53:17.262
Ooh.

53:18.996 --> 53:23.301
What have you
given me, Doctor ?
Why can't I think straight ?

53:23.334 --> 53:26.937
Thorazine.
It calms you down.

53:31.976 --> 53:33.811
What happens
to him there ?

53:35.212 --> 53:37.948
He dies.

53:37.982 --> 53:40.985
[ Sobbing ]
Doctor--

53:41.018 --> 53:46.424
don't you get it, Doctor ?
401. room 401.

53:46.457 --> 53:49.694
How many times
do I have to say it ?

53:49.727 --> 53:52.129
So you dreamed
that Paul died.

53:52.162 --> 53:55.366
I dreamed it
and it happens.

53:57.067 --> 53:59.003
It's going to happen.

53:59.036 --> 54:03.140
Can't you get it through
your thick psychiatric skull ?

54:03.173 --> 54:07.712
The man I love is dead
and I'm left in this
god-awful place alone.

54:10.080 --> 54:14.051
Hello ?
You mean he's dead
to you, Claire.

54:14.084 --> 54:20.257
No, no, I mean dead like
rebecca. how many ways
can I fucking say it ?

54:21.459 --> 54:22.527
Do--

54:24.795 --> 54:28.032
- what the fuck ?
- [ silverman ]
It's called grief.

54:28.065 --> 54:31.068
No, no,
it's Paul this time.

54:32.202 --> 54:35.239
Please.
God, listen to me.

54:36.441 --> 54:38.576
[ Whimpering ]
What's this ?

54:38.609 --> 54:40.177
- [ Yelps ]
- [ Grunts ] listen to me !

54:40.210 --> 54:42.146
- [ Barking ]
- hi, paul !

54:42.179 --> 54:43.581
- [ Groans ]
- shit !

54:44.682 --> 54:46.417
[ Alarm ringing ]

54:50.220 --> 54:52.056
[ Indistinct shouting ]

54:52.089 --> 54:55.326
Listen to me !
Oh ! no !
Come on. get up.

54:58.496 --> 55:00.698
Come on !
Aah ! aah !

55:00.731 --> 55:02.433
Listen !

55:02.467 --> 55:05.436
Listen to me !

55:06.437 --> 55:09.173
Listen !

55:09.206 --> 55:12.777
[ Rosco ] okay, we're going
to give you something
to relax. All right, turn her.

55:13.511 --> 55:14.845
All right,
get her down.

55:15.980 --> 55:19.550
Please, let me go !
Just relax.

55:19.584 --> 55:22.052
Please, no.
We're going to give you
something. take it easy.

55:33.063 --> 55:35.400
Brought you some hot tea,
honey.

55:35.433 --> 55:37.702
It'll still be warm.

55:37.735 --> 55:42.740
I'm sorry.
Do I know you ?
You're sharin' a room with me.

55:42.773 --> 55:46.611
They asked me
to keep an eye on you.
I don't remember.

55:46.644 --> 55:49.614
You got some people
in your head.
Hmm.

56:41.966 --> 56:43.333
[ Clatter ]

56:46.604 --> 56:49.540
What's the matter, honey ?
You don't like the pattern ?

56:59.316 --> 57:00.818
[ Whispering ]
Can you keep a secret ?

57:01.752 --> 57:03.253
[ Whispering ]
Probably.

57:04.955 --> 57:07.124
You won't think
I'm crazy ?

57:07.157 --> 57:11.061
[ Chuckling ] Probably
! I mean, look at you.
That man in my head...

57:11.095 --> 57:14.164
Was in this hospital
when he was a boy.
How do you know ?

57:15.332 --> 57:19.637
He stayed in this room.
He wrote that.

57:21.672 --> 57:25.676
His name's
Vivian Thompson.
Ooh, la, la. [ Chuckles ]

57:29.947 --> 57:32.750
Did anyone ever
get out of here ?

57:32.783 --> 57:37.655
I wouldn't start
thinkin' that.
I'm not talking about me.

57:37.688 --> 57:42.459
I'm talking about
somebody else.
It's not that difficult.

57:42.493 --> 57:46.263
When you've been here as long
as I have, you get to know
the language of the place.

57:49.667 --> 57:51.068
Go to sleep.

58:08.653 --> 58:12.289
- [ girl ]
Hi ! what's your name ?
- [ woman ] Ruby !

58:12.322 --> 58:14.592
Oh, sorry.
I gotta go.

58:15.459 --> 58:18.062
Ruby !

58:18.095 --> 58:20.297
Come on.
I'm runnin' late.

58:20.330 --> 58:23.400
School time.
Mommy's in a hurry now.
You're not my mommy.

58:23.433 --> 58:25.402
[ Claire ]
He's out there, hunting--

58:25.435 --> 58:27.705
Looking for
another little girl.

58:27.738 --> 58:31.308
Guess what her name is,
doctor. Ruby.

58:32.943 --> 58:35.145
And what color is Ruby,
Claire ?

58:35.179 --> 58:38.348
Ruby's not a color, Doctor.
Ruby's a girl.

58:38.382 --> 58:43.387
Red... Why are you obsessed
with that color, Claire ?

58:43.420 --> 58:46.757
I'm not obsessed,
I'm possessed, Doctor.

58:46.791 --> 58:50.661
He's feeding me dreams
bit by bit.

58:50.695 --> 58:52.563
Why's that, Claire ?

58:52.597 --> 58:57.034
Maybe he's lonely.
Maybe he's lonely, Doctor.

58:58.803 --> 59:01.438
Have you a name
for him yet ?

59:01.471 --> 59:05.542
Yes, I have.
His name is Vivian.
Vivian Thompson.

59:05.576 --> 59:09.780
There's a town out there
covered in water.
Someone left him in it.

59:09.814 --> 59:11.148
He was taken
to this hospital.

59:11.181 --> 59:15.820
He stayed in my room
and he's feeding me dreams.

59:15.853 --> 59:17.855
Why do you think that is,
doctor ?

59:19.023 --> 59:23.928
Because he wants to stop.
He wants me to stop him.

59:23.961 --> 59:26.430
It sounds psychotic to you,
doesn't it ?

59:26.463 --> 59:28.833
I didn't use that word,
Claire. you did.

59:28.866 --> 59:31.001
But follow it through,
doctor, psychotic or not.

59:31.035 --> 59:36.106
I've gotta let him p
ossess me-- surrender--

59:36.140 --> 59:38.809
let him take me to him.

59:38.843 --> 59:44.281
So what does that make me ?
Psychotic ? delusional ?
Obsessional ? all three ?

59:44.314 --> 59:48.585
If you admit to yourself
that it's delusional, Claire,
we might be getting someplace.

01:00:09.073 --> 01:00:11.909
So, what's it say
on the wall, ethel ?

01:00:13.811 --> 01:00:15.145
It's some kind
of nursery rhyme.

01:00:15.179 --> 01:00:16.947
So, I'm not insane ?

01:00:20.317 --> 01:00:22.653
Not many of us are,
honey.

01:00:23.553 --> 01:00:26.523
Go to sleep.
That's a good idea.

01:00:26.556 --> 01:00:30.861
Sleep's the only way to reach
him. he's out there somewhere
hunting another little girl,

01:00:30.895 --> 01:00:32.296
and I've gotta stop him.

01:00:35.165 --> 01:00:39.269
[ Sighs ] whatever happens,
though, promise me one THING:
Don't wake me up.

01:01:28.986 --> 01:01:30.354
[ Panting ]

01:01:58.615 --> 01:01:59.884
[ Gasps ]

01:02:06.156 --> 01:02:07.624
[ Screaming ]

01:02:13.363 --> 01:02:15.299
[ Screaming continues ]

01:02:38.655 --> 01:02:40.457
My apologies, Claire.

01:02:42.426 --> 01:02:43.627
Aah !

01:04:36.306 --> 01:04:37.707
[ Grunting ]

01:05:48.078 --> 01:05:52.449
[ Rosco ]
That's it, jodie.
Let the medication do the job.

01:05:52.482 --> 01:05:54.351
You just relax and sleep.

01:05:55.185 --> 01:05:56.720
You'll be fine.

01:06:19.109 --> 01:06:21.145
Oh ! excuse me.

01:06:26.416 --> 01:06:28.218
[ Crickets chirping ]

01:06:34.924 --> 01:06:36.660
[ Engine starting ]

01:06:44.101 --> 01:06:45.735
[ Brakes squeal ]

01:06:50.607 --> 01:06:52.509
Hey. you need a lift ?

01:06:53.577 --> 01:06:55.245
I'm waitin' for Lucy.

01:06:55.279 --> 01:06:58.415
Everything all right ?
No, I...

01:06:59.783 --> 01:07:02.752
Locked myself
out of my car.

01:07:02.786 --> 01:07:05.855
You wanna come back
to the office ?
You can use the phone.

01:07:05.889 --> 01:07:09.493
Uh, I have a spare,
uh, set...

01:07:09.959 --> 01:07:12.396
At a garage.

01:07:12.429 --> 01:07:15.165
If you're going out,
you could drop me.

01:07:16.466 --> 01:07:18.968
Which garage ?
The one down the road.

01:07:20.837 --> 01:07:23.673
Got your I.d. ?
It's locked in the car.

01:07:24.608 --> 01:07:26.310
All right. Hop in.

01:07:33.483 --> 01:07:37.854
So, uh, do you
want to get a drink
or something like that ?

01:07:38.822 --> 01:07:41.158
Yeah, maybe.
Whatever you wanna do.

01:07:53.170 --> 01:07:56.440
[ Siren wailing ]
[ Police radio chatter,
indistinct ]

01:07:56.473 --> 01:08:00.410
Could we have
some music ?
Music ? sure.

01:08:01.845 --> 01:08:06.583
[ Radio clicking ]
*The You I've Come To Know

01:08:07.951 --> 01:08:09.085
* [ Continues,
Indistinct ]
You work nights.

01:08:09.119 --> 01:08:13.157
- Uh, yeah.
- What's your name ?

01:08:13.190 --> 01:08:16.725
Vivienne.
What's yours ?
Walter.

01:08:19.496 --> 01:08:22.765
That's a nice name, vivienne.
Hey, how you spell that ?

01:08:23.399 --> 01:08:25.635
V-i-v-i-e-n-n-e.

01:08:30.939 --> 01:08:33.542
Can't keep your eyes off me,
can you ?

01:08:33.577 --> 01:08:36.979
Off what, Vivienne ?
My legs.

01:08:39.549 --> 01:08:41.885
Pity to leave you so soon,
Vivienne.

01:08:41.917 --> 01:08:45.322
Well...
I'm in no real hurry.

01:08:46.622 --> 01:08:48.591
Well, what do you know ?

01:08:49.626 --> 01:08:51.094
Neither am I.

01:08:53.863 --> 01:08:57.867
You've been eating those knees
the whole way.

01:08:57.901 --> 01:09:02.538
Shouldn't your eyes
have been on the road ?
I suppose they should've.

01:09:04.808 --> 01:09:07.010
You can kiss me
if you want.

01:09:07.977 --> 01:09:10.314
Don't mind if I do.

01:09:13.450 --> 01:09:15.519
[ Giggling ]

01:09:15.551 --> 01:09:18.020
What the fuck ?
[ Laughing ]

01:09:19.988 --> 01:09:21.725
Two things, Walter.

01:09:21.758 --> 01:09:25.694
ONE: get out of the car
really slowly.
Mm-hmm.

01:09:25.729 --> 01:09:30.334
TWO: you get your ass
back to stapleton
and tell Silverman... Mm-hmm.

01:09:30.367 --> 01:09:32.902
To check out
the Carlton hotel.

01:09:47.417 --> 01:09:49.051
Why are we here ?

01:09:49.653 --> 01:09:51.988
That's my home.

01:09:52.020 --> 01:09:54.258
A lake ?
You live in a lake ?

01:09:57.160 --> 01:09:59.629
Did once.
[ Gunshot ]

01:10:08.071 --> 01:10:09.539
[ Splashing ]

01:10:32.128 --> 01:10:34.364
[ Whispering ]
Where did you go, Vivian ?

01:10:36.733 --> 01:10:38.835
Please, please don't
leave me now.

01:10:42.906 --> 01:10:44.374
[ Footsteps ]

01:11:04.060 --> 01:11:06.763
Wanna come over to
my house, Claire ?
Uh-huh.

01:11:07.764 --> 01:11:09.466
Yeah.

01:11:09.499 --> 01:11:11.601
I have to warn you,
it's haunted.

01:11:12.836 --> 01:11:14.638
Who's it haunted by ?

01:11:15.271 --> 01:11:16.640
You.

01:11:37.661 --> 01:11:40.063
I'll show you how
to get there.
You can drive now.

01:11:48.672 --> 01:11:53.610
Vivian, is there a girl
in your house called Ruby ?

01:11:53.643 --> 01:11:56.045
Ruby ? Yeah.

01:11:58.682 --> 01:12:03.086
She's dying
to meet you.
Oh, God.

01:12:03.119 --> 01:12:06.189
You thought it was
a real orchard, huh ?

01:12:06.222 --> 01:12:08.625
That's the thing about DREAMS:
They're always right...

01:12:09.893 --> 01:12:11.961
And always wrong.

01:12:17.066 --> 01:12:20.804
You have to drive inside.
Okay ? I'll open the door.

01:12:49.065 --> 01:12:51.200
You know this place,
don't you, Claire ?

01:12:57.140 --> 01:13:00.510
Yes.
You know the funny thing ?

01:13:01.277 --> 01:13:03.212
What's the funny thing ?

01:13:03.246 --> 01:13:07.784
I know you got a gun tucked
in the band of the
nurse's dress you're wearing.

01:13:09.018 --> 01:13:11.354
I do ?
You do !

01:13:11.387 --> 01:13:15.358
And it's not very nice,
you meetin' Ruby with
a gun in your dress.

01:13:15.391 --> 01:13:18.294
Might get her upset.
Might get me upset...

01:13:19.328 --> 01:13:21.097
And bring the apples
down on all of us.

01:13:22.799 --> 01:13:26.436
Where is Ruby ?
Ubi est Ruby ?

01:13:27.771 --> 01:13:30.540
I'm not tellin'
till you gimme the gun.

01:13:41.250 --> 01:13:44.721
- you know what happens
when the apples fall ?
- I don't.

01:13:52.962 --> 01:13:56.766
*First The Tide

01:13:58.167 --> 01:14:02.005
[ Clatter ]
*Rushes In

01:14:03.372 --> 01:14:07.276
*Plants A Kiss

01:14:08.111 --> 01:14:12.281
*On The Shore

01:14:12.315 --> 01:14:15.985
*Then Rolls

01:14:16.019 --> 01:14:17.521
I'm so, so...
* [ Continues, Indistinct ]

01:14:17.554 --> 01:14:20.824
Sorry, sorry,
sorry, Claire.

01:14:22.325 --> 01:14:24.360
All I wanted was a family.

01:14:26.295 --> 01:14:30.266
I knew there was
a dreamer out there like me,
'cause I was dreamin' of her.

01:14:30.299 --> 01:14:32.368
I wanted her
to be my family.

01:14:34.370 --> 01:14:35.705
And I took her little girl.

01:14:37.507 --> 01:14:41.745
And the little girl cried
and hollered,

01:14:43.246 --> 01:14:46.916
and I punished her
like any dad would.

01:14:48.885 --> 01:14:51.054
And she was lying...
[ Sobbing ]

01:14:51.087 --> 01:14:54.090
Quiet, beautiful...

01:14:55.291 --> 01:14:57.060
But like a doll now.

01:14:59.128 --> 01:15:01.698
That's the part
I'm sorry for.
[ Gasping ]

01:15:01.731 --> 01:15:04.233
But I'm gonna
make it up to you.

01:15:04.267 --> 01:15:07.236
I'm gonna work...
Real hard.

01:15:08.504 --> 01:15:10.106
Make it perfect.

01:15:11.507 --> 01:15:15.511
I'm not gonna get upset
anymore now that
I've got you here,

01:15:15.545 --> 01:15:19.215
and I got us Ruby
for a daughter now.

01:15:20.249 --> 01:15:24.888
Claire and Vivian and Ruby.
[ Chuckles ]

01:15:24.921 --> 01:15:29.358
Did you-- did you get
upset with Ruby, Vivian ?

01:15:29.392 --> 01:15:30.927
Not yet. not yet.
Did you ?

01:15:30.960 --> 01:15:33.630
Are you gonna
get upset with me ?

01:15:35.431 --> 01:15:38.635
Not if you love me
like Mama loves Dad.
Will you do that, Claire ?

01:15:40.003 --> 01:15:42.405
I'll do that, Vivian.

01:15:44.774 --> 01:15:46.242
I'll do that.

01:15:47.877 --> 01:15:49.913
You wouldn't just pretend.

01:15:50.980 --> 01:15:52.782
How could I pretend ?

01:15:55.151 --> 01:15:58.354
How could I pretend
with you, Vivian ?

01:15:58.387 --> 01:16:01.357
You know me
inside and out.

01:16:01.390 --> 01:16:03.593
Things are
gonna be perfect...

01:16:04.961 --> 01:16:06.930
When I see Ruby.

01:16:08.164 --> 01:16:11.000
As perfect as they can be
in this valley of tears.

01:16:23.279 --> 01:16:27.316
Oh, Lordy.
What the fuck is this ?

01:16:27.350 --> 01:16:30.820
Her dream, Rosco.
Your nightmare.

01:16:34.323 --> 01:16:37.927
[ Vivian ]
Ruby, guess who's here ?
Say hi to Ruby, Claire.

01:16:43.733 --> 01:16:46.870
Hello, Ruby.
Are you a ghost ?

01:16:46.903 --> 01:16:51.340
- no, I'm not.
- she was only a ghost
when she wasn't here.

01:16:51.374 --> 01:16:53.677
Now that she's
here she's just
plain old Claire.

01:16:53.710 --> 01:16:57.380
Why don't you go down in
the garden and show Ruby
that you're not a ghost ?

01:16:59.615 --> 01:17:03.386
He said you were coming.
You took a long time.

01:17:03.419 --> 01:17:07.724
I know. It was gettin'
kinda lonesome here with
just the two of us, huh ?

01:17:07.757 --> 01:17:11.127
I suppose.
This is Marge.

01:17:11.160 --> 01:17:14.831
