[ Rosco ]
Who ?

01:17:29.779 --> 01:17:34.050
Vivian Thompson.
He escaped through that grate.
Murdered a nurse.

01:17:34.083 --> 01:17:37.420
- when ?
- twenty-five years ago.
October 1972.

01:17:37.453 --> 01:17:39.723
I'm lost, Doctor.
Join the club.

01:17:41.524 --> 01:17:43.927
He killed her daughter.

01:17:43.960 --> 01:17:48.765
