Cat got your tongue ?

01:20:21.250 --> 01:20:24.520
*Anyone Else But Me
You're worse than your
goddamn daddy !

01:20:24.553 --> 01:20:28.457
*Don't Sit Under
The Apple Tree With
anyone else but me *

01:20:28.491 --> 01:20:31.961
