Are you tied too tight ?

01:21:17.206 --> 01:21:19.675
I'd loosen it,
but he might get mad again.

01:21:19.708 --> 01:21:23.012
I'd never seen him
mad before.
[ Vivian ] Ruby !

01:21:27.216 --> 01:21:28.884
