for bed, I--

01:23:06.849 --> 01:23:08.484
I believed her.

01:23:08.517 --> 01:23:11.187
Sorry if I'm moody.
It's just been a long day.

01:23:11.220 --> 01:23:13.356
Things didn't
turn out the way...

01:23:15.158 --> 01:23:16.959
