01:24:18.821 --> 01:24:21.490
I dreamed my mommy
was dead in the lake...

01:24:23.859 --> 01:24:25.861
And she had your face.

01:24:25.894 --> 01:24:28.864
[ Gasps ]
[ Sobbing ]

01:24:28.897 --> 01:24:30.866
