01:25:43.806 --> 01:25:47.009
Come here. now, you gotta
be brave now, Ruby.

01:25:47.042 --> 01:25:49.945
You gotta be brave,
honey.
Yes. you gotta come with me.

01:25:49.978 --> 01:25:54.183
