- aah !

01:27:17.366 --> 01:27:19.435
Gonna kiss
and make it better !

01:27:19.468 --> 01:27:21.304
[ Yelping ]
[ Growls ]

01:27:21.337 --> 01:27:26.174
Every couple has their
problems. Thing is, we have
to talk ! [ Grunts ]

01:27:26.742 --> 01:27:28.444
